  "elapsed_s": 7.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Into working within the houses?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My older sister left '37, 1937.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We still by the north, old house.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And '39 we needed to move to Tokaj.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I start right-- I couldn't-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] about '38, 1938.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that was help for my parents, too, because earn some money.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because my middle sister, the third one, was helping in the house, and cooking, and you know-- the house fraulein, they called it-- [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And my younger sister went to the high school.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And when we moved to-- my mother was so sick she don't want to look for an apartment.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I went with my father to look for the apartment to move from there because--",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] those days, when they have some loan in your house-- somehow, you know, five children-- and my father wrote some [NON-ENGLISH], and people doesn't paid.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So they was every house.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the bank got the house without we know it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my two older sisters sended the money to the bank.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But meanwhile came the Jewish law.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Even one, they, I think, owned the bank.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I went-- I was I think 18 or something. 19-- to the office in Budapest, and I asked them when my father was first war-- how come they don't giving living there?",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So somebody, a Gentile person, got the house.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So my older sister of my mother, she lived with us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And she said, I'm not going to go out in this house alive.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "She died.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "First time I saw a dead person in the house.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So we went to the city.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] we get back our-- they take away our license the tavern, because the big-- and then, a couple of months later, they give it back.",
      "word_count": 30
    }
  ],
